   1:				; *******************************************************
   2:				; * Bitcoin Mining for CP/M                             *
   3:				; * Version: V1.1                                       *
   4:				; * Merlin Skinner, 1/3/2026                            *
   5:				; *******************************************************
   6:				;
   7:				; V1.0 - 5/9/2022, initial version.
   8:				; V1.1 - 1/3/2026, added CP/M 3 support. Use BDOS console I/O.
   9:				;
  10:				; This program is intended to run under CP/M 2.2 or CP/M 3. It should run under
  11:				; any such system, though timing is only available when run on ZARC.
  12:				;
  13:				                title Bitcoin Mining for CP/M
  14:				;
  15:				;
  16:				;
